Now why is it so necessary for us to understand that?

00:00:15.699 --> 00:00:20.660
And what skills will help us to reach the heart of our students?

00:00:20.660 --> 00:00:25.420
Jesus gave an indication in His illustration of the Sore.

00:00:25.420 --> 00:00:31.940
It's found in Matthew chapter 13, and we'll read verse 19.

00:00:31.940 --> 00:00:41.259
It says, where anyone hears the word of the kingdom, but does not get the sense of it,

00:00:41.259 --> 00:00:47.539
the wicked one comes and snatches away what has been sown in his heart.

00:00:47.539 --> 00:00:55.659
So the word of the kingdom is likened to seeds and the soil to the figurative heart.

00:00:55.659 --> 00:00:59.259
Now the figurative heart represents what a person is inside.

00:00:59.259 --> 00:01:05.459
It involves his feelings, his affections, his desires, his motives, also what he thinks

00:01:05.459 --> 00:01:10.340
about and how those thoughts affect decisions in his life.

00:01:10.340 --> 00:01:16.420
If you look back at verse 19, Jesus said that the seed in this case didn't grow because

00:01:16.420 --> 00:01:21.099
the individual didn't get the sense of the good news.

00:01:21.099 --> 00:01:27.299
Now Jesus has given all of us this assignment to make disciples of people of all nations

00:01:27.379 --> 00:01:28.980
and baptizing them.

00:01:28.980 --> 00:01:35.260
So our teaching needs to help our students get the sense of the good news, and that's

00:01:35.260 --> 00:01:38.219
going to move them to action.

00:01:38.219 --> 00:01:46.340
Proverbs chapter 3 and verse 1 highlights an importance of this type of teaching to us.

00:01:46.340 --> 00:01:50.939
It's Proverbs 3 and verse 1.

00:01:50.939 --> 00:01:58.379
Jesus says, my son, do not forget my teaching and may your heart observe my commandments.

00:01:58.379 --> 00:02:04.219
So obedience to God must come from the heart as it indicates.

00:02:04.219 --> 00:02:11.219
So brothers and sisters, it's our responsibility to learn how to reach the heart of our students

00:02:11.219 --> 00:02:17.979
so that their thinking, their feelings, their reasonings will move them to be obedient

00:02:17.979 --> 00:02:20.219
to Jehovah God.

