Does a little child always understand why mum and dad warns them not to do certain things?

00:03:37.150 --> 00:03:39.150
Probably not.

00:03:39.150 --> 00:03:42.550
So why all the rules and warnings?

00:03:42.550 --> 00:03:46.849
Well, they love them, don't they?

00:03:46.849 --> 00:04:01.770
And so if Jehovah loves you, it often takes time to appreciate why Jehovah asked certain things of us.

00:04:02.770 --> 00:04:13.870
