00:04:13.870 --> 00:04:18.540
The real question is, do you trust him?

00:04:18.540 --> 00:04:26.040
I won't do.

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:27.040
I really do.

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:42.399
This was a good example of how a Bible study conductor reaches the heart of a student.

00:04:42.399 --> 00:04:50.399
Anita was calmly helping Jade to link what she was learning in her study to her relationship with Jehovah God.

00:04:50.399 --> 00:04:58.399
