And Proverbs 20 and verse 5.

00:07:30.399 --> 00:07:39.399
It says, the thoughts of a man's heart are like deep waters, but the discerning man draws them out.

00:07:39.399 --> 00:07:44.399
And so the thoughts of a student are not always easily discernible.

00:07:44.399 --> 00:07:53.399
Yes, it really takes a skilled teacher to draw those out like deep waters the verse indicates.

